WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.719
Justin.

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.320
I just thought I'd stop by and say goodbye.

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.839
I heard you were going back to Smallville tomorrow.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Yeah, Smallville.

00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:37.039
How's it going?

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:47.379
