00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:22.200
What's your fault?

00:09:22.220 --> 00:09:22.240
What's your fault?

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:22.259
What's your fault?

00:09:22.259 --> 00:09:22.279
What's your fault?

00:09:22.279 --> 00:09:22.360
What's your fault?

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.180
All those years, I thought you loved me.

00:09:29.800 --> 00:09:31.139
But you were just in it for the money.

00:09:33.940 --> 00:09:38.060
I know you're angry with me, and you have every right to be, but we need to talk.

00:09:41.700 --> 00:09:44.220
I can't believe there's anything you'd say that would interest me.

00:09:47.320 --> 00:09:48.019
