I love you, too.

00:09:58.340 --> 00:09:59.720
This one's definitely my favorite strip.

00:09:59.800 --> 00:09:59.960
Really?

00:10:00.019 --> 00:10:00.279
Yes.

00:10:00.379 --> 00:10:00.759
Mike.

00:10:01.420 --> 00:10:02.080
Hey, guys.

00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:03.480
Hey.

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:04.680
You know Justin?

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:05.259
Yeah.

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:06.399
Of course.

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:07.019
Welcome back.

00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:08.100
How you feeling?

00:10:08.639 --> 00:10:11.300
Oh, I'm just kind of taking it one day at a time.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.980
Did they ever find the driver who hit you?

00:10:15.580 --> 00:10:15.980
No.

00:10:16.259 --> 00:10:17.980
No, I couldn't really give the police that much.

00:10:18.019 --> 00:10:19.480
I didn't remember anything for a long time.

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:20.700
Well, what do you remember?

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:22.080
Um.

00:10:22.220 --> 00:10:24.980
A little bit of the license plate. DDI.

00:10:25.460 --> 00:10:26.420
We should look into it.

00:10:26.460 --> 00:10:27.240
You should call the police.

00:10:27.399 --> 00:10:28.980
If we find something, we'll pass it on.

00:10:33.300 --> 00:10:33.660
Okay.

00:10:36.879 --> 00:10:40.000
Anyway, I talked to Lex. He scored us two tickets to the conference.

00:10:40.580 --> 00:10:43.879
Oh, don't worry about it, Clark. Justin's already signed up, so I'm going as his guest.

00:10:44.100 --> 00:10:45.259
Yeah, or we could all go together.

00:10:45.740 --> 00:10:49.500
No. Um, Clark's not that interested in journalism anyway.

00:10:52.220 --> 00:10:55.500
Right, okay. Uh, I should probably get going. Listen...

00:10:55.500 --> 00:11:09.519
Thank you.

00:11:19.019 --> 00:11:19.500
Hi.

00:11:19.500 --> 00:11:21.300
Hey, Clark. Did you run around?

00:11:21.399 --> 00:11:22.200
I wanted to order some more.

00:11:22.220 --> 00:11:22.720
I want to order pies.

00:11:22.980 --> 00:11:24.600
She's a class. I can help you.

00:11:25.220 --> 00:11:28.200
Didn't expect to see you here. I thought you'd be helping Chloe proof the latest edition.

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:29.259
She had enough help.

00:11:30.040 --> 00:11:31.200
Are you two still fighting?

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.019
