00:11:34.080 --> 00:11:35.720
I know. Caught it yesterday at the career fair.

00:11:37.300 --> 00:11:38.399
What's going on with you two?

00:11:40.759 --> 00:11:41.540
Chloe likes me.

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:44.820
So how do you feel about her?

00:11:46.660 --> 00:11:48.180
Like maybe we could be more than friends?

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:51.879
What?

00:11:51.879 --> 00:11:52.180
When I saw her with you...

00:11:52.220 --> 00:11:53.720
When I saw Justin today, I got kinda...

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:54.220
Jealous?

00:11:54.220 --> 00:11:59.220
It's like you find out this secret and it colors everything.

00:11:59.220 --> 00:12:03.220
I just can't believe I never saw it before.

00:12:03.220 --> 00:12:08.220
Sometimes the right person can be right in front of your eyes and you never even know it.

00:12:16.220 --> 00:12:19.220
Uh, so how many pies did you want?

00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:20.220
A dozen.

00:12:20.220 --> 00:12:21.220
A dozen?

00:12:21.220 --> 00:12:21.980
Yeah.

00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:23.220
That's good.

00:12:23.220 --> 00:12:25.220
How's Whitney? I hear his dad's feeling better.

00:12:27.220 --> 00:12:28.220
He's great.

00:12:31.220 --> 00:12:32.220
Everything okay?

00:12:34.220 --> 00:12:35.220
Never better.

00:12:38.220 --> 00:12:39.220
