00:23:45.980 --> 00:23:48.280
It hit me so hard it felt like I'd been broken in half.

00:23:48.920 --> 00:23:50.300
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:23:53.520 --> 00:23:55.200
Because I remember lying in the street,

00:23:55.800 --> 00:23:56.980
blood dripping into my eyes,

00:23:57.060 --> 00:23:58.380
